summary: Heartless Kinetao enb got updated with a unique cinematic shader and even more balanced lighting. Ultra-atmospheric, cinematic enb preset with totally unique shaders you wont find in any other enb.
descriptionHtml:
[center]LaBeatbeatbox presents

a finetuned cinematic enb preset



[size=5][u][b]Heartless Kinetao Cinegraph ENB

[img]http://static-1.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/59529-2-1414711897.jpg[/img]
[/b][/u][/size]



[/center]This enb preset delivers pure eye candy. Be prepared...
This page is work in progress. More text, more information and more pictures coming soon.


Not compatible with CoT or any other weather or lighting condition altering mod.
If you use said mods, deactivate them with your modmanager.




[center][img]http://static-1.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/59529-1-1414711984.jpg[/img]

[/center]

To install this enb, first remove all enb / sweet fx files from your skyrim folder ( if you used enb / sweet fx before )
You will need the 132 binaries:
[url=http://enbdev.com/mod_tesskyrim_v0132.htm]0.132 binaries from enbdev.com[/url]
pick the d3d9.dll file from the wrapper folder. (not the injector)
and put them into your skyrim main folder

download my preset and put all enb files in your skyrim main folder.


[center][img]http://static-1.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/59529-3-1414711984.jpg[/img][/center]
